        "TileImage": "$($repository f2f8b9ce-9850-43bc-aaff-c5a7155ac593).Image",
        "Description": "SquidwardBobi woke up to a calm, peaceful morning and smiled. He made himself a quiet breakfast, then spent hours playing his clarinet, each note echoing beautifully through the reef.\r\rLater, he took a slow walk, enjoying the gentle currents and the soft sway of the kelp. No interruptions, no chaos—just calm and control.\r\rAs the sun faded, SquidwardBobi relaxed at home, satisfied. For once, everything felt just right, and he truly enjoyed the simple, peaceful life he had built.",
